products.name: Yamaha F310 Acoustic Guitar
products.description: The Yamaha F310 is a full-size steel-string acoustic guitar that offers great playability and tone at an affordable price. Perfect for beginners and intermediate players.

products.name: Fender Stratocaster Electric Guitar
products.description: The Fender Stratocaster is one of the most iconic electric guitars ever created. Known for its versatile tone and comfortable playability, it's a favorite among guitarists of all genres.

products.name: Roland FP-30X Digital Piano
products.description: The Roland FP-30X is a compact digital piano with authentic piano touch and tone. Features 88 weighted keys, built-in speakers, and Bluetooth connectivity.

products.name: Yamaha PSR-E373 Portable Keyboard
products.description: The Yamaha PSR-E373 is a 61-key portable keyboard with touch-sensitive keys, 622 voices, and built-in lessons. Perfect for beginners and intermediate players.

products.name: Yamaha Stage Custom Drum Set
products.description: The Yamaha Stage Custom is a professional-grade drum set that offers exceptional sound quality and durability. Includes bass drum, toms, and snare drum.

products.name: Fernandes Retrorocket X Electric Guitar
products.description: The Fernandes Retrorocket X is a vintage-inspired electric guitar with modern features. Features a comfortable body shape, powerful pickups, and smooth playability.

products.name: Fender Jazz Bass
products.description: The Fender Jazz Bass is one of the most versatile and popular bass guitars ever created. Known for its distinctive tone and comfortable playability.

products.name: Roland TD-17KVX Electronic Drum Kit
products.description: The Roland TD-17KVX is a premium electronic drum kit that offers realistic feel and sound. Features mesh heads, natural playing response, and built-in coaching functions.

products.name: Gibson Les Paul Standard Electric Guitar
products.description: The Gibson Les Paul Standard is a legendary electric guitar known for its rich, warm tone and sustain. Features a mahogany body with a maple top, rosewood fingerboard, and Burstbucker pickups.

products.name: Ibanez RG550 Electric Guitar
products.description: The Ibanez RG550 is a high-performance electric guitar designed for speed and precision. Features a Super Wizard neck, Edge tremolo, and V7/V8 pickups.

products.name: Martin D-28 Acoustic Guitar
products.description: The Martin D-28 is a classic dreadnought acoustic guitar with a rich history. Features a solid Sitka spruce top, East Indian rosewood back and sides, and a mahogany neck.

products.name: Taylor 214ce Acoustic-Electric Guitar
products.description: The Taylor 214ce is a versatile acoustic-electric guitar with a Grand Auditorium body. Features a solid Sitka spruce top, layered rosewood back and sides, and ES2 electronics.

products.name: PRS SE Custom 24 Electric Guitar
products.description: The PRS SE Custom 24 is a versatile electric guitar that delivers premium features at an affordable price. Features a maple top with mahogany back, 24-fret neck, and 85/15 'S' pickups.

products.name: Epiphone Les Paul Standard Electric Guitar
products.description: The Epiphone Les Paul Standard offers the classic Les Paul design and tone at an affordable price. Features a mahogany body with maple top, ProBucker pickups, and Grover tuners.

products.name: Squier Classic Vibe '50s Telecaster
products.description: The Squier Classic Vibe '50s Telecaster delivers authentic vintage Tele style and tone. Features a pine body, maple neck, and Fender-designed alnico single-coil pickups.

products.name: Yamaha APX600 Acoustic-Electric Guitar
products.description: The Yamaha APX600 is a thin-body acoustic-electric guitar designed for comfortable playability. Features a spruce top, die-cast tuners, and System 65A preamp with built-in tuner.

products.name: Yamaha P-125 Digital Piano
products.description: The Yamaha P-125 is a compact digital piano with 88 weighted keys and authentic piano sound. Features Yamaha's Pure CF Sound Engine, built-in speakers, and various connectivity options.

products.name: Casio Privia PX-S1000 Digital Piano
products.description: The Casio Privia PX-S1000 is the world's slimmest digital piano with 88 weighted keys. Features Smart Scaled Hammer Action Keyboard, 18 tones, and Bluetooth audio.

products.name: Nord Stage 3 88 Keyboard
products.description: The Nord Stage 3 is a flagship keyboard workstation for professional musicians. Features 88 weighted hammer action keys, three sound engines, and extensive effects section.

products.name: Korg Kronos 88 Keyboard Workstation
products.description: The Korg Kronos is a professional keyboard workstation with nine sound engines. Features 88 weighted keys, color touchscreen, and extensive sequencing capabilities.

products.name: Roland JUNO-DS88 Synthesizer
products.description: The Roland JUNO-DS88 is a versatile synthesizer with 88 weighted keys. Features over 1,000 sounds, pattern sequencer, and USB audio/MIDI interface.

products.name: Yamaha MODX8 Synthesizer
products.description: The Yamaha MODX8 is a powerful synthesizer with 88 weighted keys. Features AWM2 and FM-X sound engines, Super Knob control, and extensive connectivity options.

products.name: Akai MPK249 MIDI Controller
products.description: The Akai MPK249 is a 49-key MIDI controller with semi-weighted keys. Features 16 MPC pads, 8 assignable knobs, and extensive DAW integration.

products.name: Novation Launchkey 49 MK3 MIDI Controller
products.description: The Novation Launchkey 49 MK3 is a 49-key MIDI controller designed for Ableton Live. Features 16 velocity-sensitive pads, 8 knobs, and deep integration with DAWs.

products.name: Arturia KeyLab 88 MK2 MIDI Controller
products.description: The Arturia KeyLab 88 MK2 is a premium 88-key MIDI controller with hammer-action keybed. Features 16 RGB pads, 9 faders, and extensive DAW integration.

products.name: Native Instruments Komplete Kontrol S88 MK2
products.description: The Native Instruments Komplete Kontrol S88 MK2 is a premium 88-key MIDI controller with Fatar keybed. Features dual color screens, light guide, and deep integration with NI software.

products.name: Pearl Export EXX725S/C Drum Set
products.description: The Pearl Export EXX725S/C is a complete 5-piece drum set with hardware. Features poplar/Asian mahogany shells, 830 series hardware, and durable finish options.

products.name: Tama Imperialstar 5-Piece Drum Set
products.description: The Tama Imperialstar is a complete 5-piece drum set with hardware and cymbals. Features 100% poplar shells, Accu-Tune bass drum hoops, and precision bearing edges.

products.name: DW Design Series 5-Piece Drum Set
products.description: The DW Design Series is a professional 5-piece drum set. Features North American maple shells, True-Pitch tuning system, and STM mounting system.

products.name: Gretsch Catalina Maple 7-Piece Drum Set
products.description: The Gretsch Catalina Maple is a versatile 7-piece drum set. Features 7-ply maple shells, 30-degree bearing edges, and GTS mounting system.

products.name: Alesis Surge Mesh Electronic Drum Kit
products.description: The Alesis Surge Mesh is an electronic drum kit with mesh heads. Features 8-inch mesh snare, three 8-inch mesh toms, and Surge Drum Module with 385 sounds.

products.name: Yamaha DTX6K-X Electronic Drum Kit
products.description: The Yamaha DTX6K-X is a premium electronic drum kit. Features TCS pads, real hi-hat stand, and DTX-PRO module with 40 preset kits.

products.name: Roland VAD306 V-Drums Acoustic Design Kit
products.description: The Roland VAD306 combines the look and feel of acoustic drums with electronic versatility. Features full-size wood shells, digital snare/ride, and TD-27 sound module.

products.name: Zildjian A Custom Cymbal Pack
products.description: The Zildjian A Custom cymbal pack includes 14-inch hi-hats, 16-inch crash, 18-inch crash, and 20-inch ride. Features brilliant finish and bright, expressive sound.

products.name: Sabian AAX Cymbal Pack
products.description: The Sabian AAX cymbal pack includes 14-inch hi-hats, 16-inch crash, 18-inch crash, and 21-inch ride. Features modern, bright sound with quick response.

products.name: Meinl HCS Cymbal Pack
products.description: The Meinl HCS cymbal pack includes 14-inch hi-hats, 16-inch crash, and 20-inch ride. Features brass alloy construction and is ideal for beginners.

products.name: Shure SM57 Instrument Microphone
products.description: The Shure SM57 is a legendary dynamic microphone for instrument recording and sound reinforcement. Features cardioid pickup pattern and rugged construction.

products.name: Focusrite Scarlett 2i2 Audio Interface
products.description: The Focusrite Scarlett 2i2 is a popular 2-in/2-out USB audio interface. Features two mic/line/instrument inputs with Scarlett preamps and 24-bit/192kHz conversion.

products.name: Boss Katana-50 MkII Guitar Amplifier
products.description: The Boss Katana-50 MkII is a versatile 50-watt guitar amplifier. Features five amp characters, over 60 effects, and USB connectivity for recording.

products.name: Fender Deluxe Molded Guitar Case
products.description: The Fender Deluxe Molded Case provides superior protection for your guitar. Features molded ABS exterior, plush interior, and TSA-approved latches.

products.name: D'Addario EXL110 Electric Guitar Strings
products.description: D'Addario EXL110 Nickel Wound Regular Light gauge strings (10-46) are D'Addario's most popular electric guitar string set. Features round wound with nickel-plated steel.

products.name: Ernie Ball Regular Slinky Guitar Strings
products.description: Ernie Ball Regular Slinky strings (10-46) are made from nickel-plated steel wire wrapped around a hex-shaped steel core wire. The most popular Slinky gauge.

products.name: Dunlop Tortex Standard Guitar Picks
products.description: Dunlop Tortex Standard picks offer the perfect combination of flexibility and control. Pack includes 12 picks in your choice of gauge.

products.name: Hercules GS414B Guitar Stand
products.description: The Hercules GS414B is a single guitar stand with auto grip system. Features foldable design, neck cradle with specially formulated foam, and stable tripod base.

products.name: Korg TM-60 Tuner Metronome
products.description: The Korg TM-60 combines a tuner and metronome in one compact device. Features wide detection range, 15 rhythm variations, and up to 120 hours of battery life.

products.name: Vic Firth 5A Drumsticks
products.description: Vic Firth 5A drumsticks are the world's most popular stick model. Features tear-drop tip, medium taper, and versatile design for various playing styles.
